      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that makes sense. so if it's attaching to the VP, the tree structure would show the PP as a daughter of the VP node, right? i'm just trying to visualize how the branching actually works out in the diagram when it's an adjunct vs a complement. can you walk me through the specific nodes?",
